Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of natural language processing (NLP) techniques to explore the pedagogical value of technical documents, which suggests a focus on computational linguistics (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The creation of an annotated corpus also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and data mining (cs.CY). Additionally, the use of deep learning techniques for automatic prediction of pedagogical roles suggests a focus on deep learning (cs.DL).
